building_description:
The Rings by PMR Property: Luxurious Sky Mansions & Sky Palaces in Jumeirah
The Rings by PMR Property is a prestigious development located on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal in Jumeirah. This premium project offers a limited collection of 5-6 bedroom Sky Mansions and 6-7 bedroom Sky Palaces, each featuring breathtaking canal views and panoramic vistas of Dubai. With starting prices from AED 59 million, The Rings promises an indulgent lifestyle with its 5-star amenities and a la carte services, set to be handed over in Q4 2025.
Key Information:

Starting Price: AED 69,000,000
Developer: PMR Property
Delivery Date: December 2025
Payment Plan: 60/40 with 5% down payment
Location: Dubai Water Canal, Jumeirah

Unit Types:

5 Bedroom Sky Mansion: 9,613 sqft
6 Bedroom Sky Mansion: 15,123 sqft
7 Bedroom Sky Palace: 19,192 sqft

Exclusive Features:

Private air-conditioned garage
Direct access via private lift
Unfurnished units with high-end finishes and equipment from brands like OBEGI, Poliform, Gaggenau, and Antonio Lupi
Private garden, home theatre, pool, and gym
Separate rooms for maid and driver
Patios for grilling
Panoramic views of the Dubai Water Canal

Prime Location: The Rings offers easy access to major roads like Al Wasl Road and Sheikh Zayed Road. Key nearby landmarks include Downtown Dubai, Dubai Mall, Dubai Opera, and Dubai International Airport. The project is also close to recreational areas like Safa Park, Jumeirah Beach, and Ras Al Khor Wildlife Sanctuary.
Additional Benefits: Upon completion, foreign buyers will be eligible for a 10-year Golden Visa, covering the property owner, their spouse, children, and domestic staff. This visa is renewable as long as the property remains owned.
The Rings by PMR Property is the epitome of luxurious living in Dubai, combining prime location, exquisite design, and unparalleled amenities.
